{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extend the winter fuel allowance for all over 60s & families with kids under-18",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "I want the Government to extend the winter fuel allowance this winter by paying energy companies \u00a3100 for each of gas & electricity per month from October to January directly to the energy companies, for anyone over 60 & families with children under 18. I believe it is affordable and can save lives.",
